{"tid":537061,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"史匹堡下部作品鎖定為《奪寶奇兵5》","createTime":"2018-01-22T11:05:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-24T06:02:29.000Z","uid":41343,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2ca60f2b22e11c235f831b195f0b23c93d992607","tid":537061,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T11:05:11.000Z","msg":"金獎導演史蒂芬史匹柏（Steven Spielberg）在 2016 年帶來童書改編《吹夢巨人》（The BFG）後，接著執導了小說改編科幻電影《一級玩家》（Ready Player One），不過在漫長的後製等待過程中，史匹柏又接下了取材真人實事的《郵報：密戰》（The Post），並且率先在 2017 年度獎季登場。<br />\n<br />\n而在史蒂芬史匹柏為數眾多的執導計畫中，根據 Deadline 報導，他已經鎖定了兩部電影作為下一部優先執導的作品，其一是奇幻冒險電影「印第安納瓊斯系列」的第五部續集（Indiana Jones 5），其二則是史匹柏夢想許久的音樂劇電影《西城故事》（West Side Story）的全新重拍。<br />\n<br />\n目前《印第安納瓊斯5》已經排定在 2020 年 7 月上映，嚴格說起來還有些許空檔時間，也就是說，假使有像《郵報：密戰》這樣優秀的劇本出現的話，史匹柏也不排除在《印第安納瓊斯5》之前以最快的速度來拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n然而原本也將以最速件執行的《The Kidnapping of Edgardo Mortara》現在則稍有擱置，此片是改編自普立茲獎得主大衛柯澤（David Kertzer）的同名著作，由《林肯》（Lincoln）編劇東尼庫許納（Tony Kushner）執筆劇本，描述在 1858 年的義大利波隆那，一名猶太男孩被強行從家人身邊帶走，並將他偷偷受洗以基督教徒撫養養大。<br />\n<br />\n早先已選定從《間諜橋》（Bridge of Spies）開始多次合作的馬克瑞蘭斯（Mark Rylance）以及奧斯卡伊薩克（Oscar Isaac）主演，但據 Deadline 報導，此片目前暫無進度是因為找不到適合的人選來演出片中的猶太男孩。<br />\n<br />\n而史蒂芬史匹柏接下來將與觀眾見面的兩部執導電影《郵報：密戰》與《一級玩家》將分別在 2 月 23 日、3 月 29 日台灣上映。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hypesphere.com/archives/97351\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hypesphere.com%2Farchives%2F97351&d=oEo0AzALoOssHNBaD4ojur%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=b6a12e31\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hypesphere.com/archives/97351</a><br />\n<br />\n真係有必要拍？"},{"pid":"04776af2ce85600dab829708ebfdba04c73d0a8a","tid":537061,"uid":7803,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T11:09:45.000Z","msg":"叫Harrison 出黎客串引下人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 唔好再拍，爛咗就仆街"},{"pid":"6400758aad128fb6602abbc862a919af1f072f05","tid":537061,"uid":28619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T11:15:43.000Z","msg":"拍後生版既 Sean Connery"},{"pid":"b770bd3b14bdeef0af434954d38f3eb2b6f4d93d","tid":537061,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04776af2ce85600dab829708ebfdba04c73d0a8a","tid":537061,"uid":7803,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T11:09:45.000Z","msg":"叫Harrison 出黎客串引下人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 唔好再拍，爛咗就仆街"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T11:19:18.000Z","msg":"應該唔係客串<br />\n仍然係主演"},{"pid":"72a481af48ae844a70e8e68d4cf984f4a4079631","tid":537061,"uid":7803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b770bd3b14bdeef0af434954d38f3eb2b6f4d93d","tid":537061,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04776af2ce85600dab829708ebfdba04c73d0a8a","tid":537061,"uid":7803,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T11:09:45.000Z","msg":"叫Harrison 出黎客串引下人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 唔好再拍，爛咗就仆街"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T11:19:18.000Z","msg":"應該唔係客串<br />\n仍然係主演"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T15:34:45.000Z","msg":"75歲啦。。。"},{"pid":"14090ca74604abfc7f2294b7fda800d81bc4545b","tid":537061,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T15:53:29.000Z","msg":"虐老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc67f1cc82d3f6b134aecfdb491fa4654b1effb3","tid":537061,"uid":6980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T15:57:48.000Z","msg":"上一集已經爛爛地 仲黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32b0db48ba4c8847cb34f26b943647751ada39e6","tid":537061,"uid":13946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T15:58:44.000Z","msg":"屌唔好啦，明明第三集個結局係完美<br />\n屌你史匹堡拍第啲嘢啦"},{"pid":"a6d4bd2e6809c17a33c4a542a6b7813cb40def92","tid":537061,"uid":13946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc67f1c